-*- text -*-

Sandia SHMEM NEWS -- history of user-visible changes.

1.2.0
-----
- Support for OpenSHMEM 1.2 specification
- Support for libfabric
- Add simple-pmi support to enable use of an external PMI-1 compliant launcher
- Add 'oshrun' launcher wrapper to normalize runs across build configurations
- Multiple bug fixes and improvements to overall stability and performance

1.0a8
-----
- Initial public release
